{
  "brandStatement": "The AD Efffects is a bespoke interior design studio creating thoughtfully crafted homes and spaces. Our work is rooted in clarity of planning, depth of detail, and a deep respect for material, craft, and context. Every project is approached as a collaboration — designed with intent, executed with rigour, and shaped around the people who live within it.",
  "story": {
    "title": "Restraint & Harmony",
    "paragraphs": [
      "Founded with a dedication to spatial purity, The AD Efffects focuses on modern minimalism, tactile materiality, and silent luxury. We reject excess to design enduring, peaceful sanctuaries.",
      "Our projects range from high-end residential estates to curated workspace branding. In every commission, we seek architectural restraint, optimizing raw wood, travertine stone, and natural illumination."
